Version:        0.05
Release:        32%{?dist}
Summary:        Simplified interface to XML::Parser
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Vendor:         Microsoft Corporation
Distribution:   Azure Linux
URL:            https://metacpan.org/release/XML-TokeParser
